<p>直听得一姐虎躯一震，<strong>现在连5000亿都不叫豪门了？</strong></p>
<p>折合王健林的5000个小目标呢！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201121/4c35aa8544d341a78a8a000cd417fc49.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>而且不知道为啥，奚梦瑶和何猷君越是营销恩爱人设，广大网友就越不买账……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201121/b42edb605e804ebb99173082aa3efb80.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
